text: Kyra Christmas (born 14 March 1997) is a female water polo player from Canada. She was a member of the Canada women's national water polo team at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 Pan American Games. She played for the University of the Pacific's women's water polo team. == References == ==Other websites== * kyra-christmas swimswam Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian water polo players
